Class CodeBlockListSnapHandler

java.lang.Object
smeen.logic.CodeBlockListSnapHandler
All Implemented Interfaces:
SnapHandler
public class CodeBlockListSnapHandler extends Object implements SnapHandler
A handler for a currently dragging code block to check if the dragging code block can be snapped to other node.

      Description copied from interface: SnapHandler
